mil.nga.giat.geowave.vector.query

Class SpatialDecimationQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.nga.giat.geowave.accumulo.query.AccumuloQuery
      • mil.nga.giat.geowave.accumulo.query.AccumuloFilteredIndexQuery
        • mil.nga.giat.geowave.accumulo.query.AccumuloConstraintsQuery
          • mil.nga.giat.geowave.vector.query.AccumuloCqlConstraintsQuery
            • mil.nga.giat.geowave.vector.query.SpatialDecimationQuery

  • public class SpatialDecimationQuery
extends AccumuloCqlConstraintsQuery
    This class extends the capabilities of a simple constraints query to perform decimation (smart pixel-based row skipping) within tablet servers. It also supports CQL filters within the tablet servers and it will only skip when a row passes the filters.
